Package: tndata
Title: Fetch datasets from the Official Tunisian Data Catalog
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Aymen", "Nasri",
      email = "aymennasrii@proton.me",
      role = c("aut", "cre", "cph")
    )
  )
Description: Simplifies access to Tunisian government open data with R. 
      Queries datasets by theme, author, or keywords, retrieves metadata, and gets structured results ready for analysis; all through the official <data.gov.tn> CKAN API.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
